alic_mga94 = 53, 386352.3979, 7381850.7689, 603.3466
alic_mga20 = 53, 386353.2343, 7381852.2986, 603.2489
alic_mga94_noellht_comp = mga2020_to_mga94(alic_mga20[0], alic_mga20[1],
    alic_mga20[2])
assert alic_mga94_noellht_comp[0] - alic_mga94[0] == 0
assert abs(alic_mga94_noellht_comp[1] - alic_mga94[1]) < 5e-05
assert abs(alic_mga94_noellht_comp[2] - alic_mga94[2]) < 5e-05
assert alic_mga94_noellht_comp[3] == 0
alic_mga94_ellht_comp = mga2020_to_mga94(alic_mga20[0], alic_mga20[1],
    alic_mga20[2], alic_mga20[3])
assert alic_mga94_ellht_comp[0] - alic_mga94[0] == 0
assert abs(alic_mga94_ellht_comp[1] - alic_mga94[1]) < 5e-05
assert abs(alic_mga94_ellht_comp[2] - alic_mga94[2]) < 5e-05
assert abs(alic_mga94_ellht_comp[3] - alic_mga94[3]) < 5e-05
